fields.product_name: Beefeater Burner for Signature series Grill
fields.description:
The Beefeater Grill Part #94735 is a premium cast stainless steel burner that sets a new standard for grilling performance and durability. This heavy-duty burner is designed to handle demanding cooking tasks, providing consistent heat distribution and efficient combustion up to 18,000 BTUs. With its robust construction and lifetime warranty, you can trust this burner to deliver reliable results meal after meal. Whether you're a seasoned grill master or just starting out, this cast stainless steel burner is the perfect upgrade for your Beefeater grill.
 

Key Features:

 Material: Cast stainless steel construction for durability and resistance to corrosion

 Compatibility: Designed to fit all Beefeater grill models
